{"tid":1715061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"盡快接小學子女回家，我唔想睇到家長被要脅的一幕","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:02:51.000Z","uid":277718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"53be6de91f5c09f1b872eb58c70125f8d5d37af4","tid":1715061,"uid":277718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"請幫推"},{"pid":"2746a355f1157313430aa15d52b3dc74987d7858","tid":1715061,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9DDrPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9DDrPs.jpg&h=fd5eb776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"}]}